el=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://alum.barnard.edu/s/1133/index.aspx?sid=1133&amp;gid=1&amp;pgid=355#classfundchair\">\"Class Officer Responsibilities\"</a> Barnard Alumnae website</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.interlakes.org/ilhs/Administration/Advisor%20Duties.pdf\">\"Class Advisor Responsibilities\"</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20110719161130/http://www.interlakes.org/ilhs/Administration/Advisor%20Duties.pdf\">Archived</a> 2011-07-19 at the <a href=\"/wiki/Wayback_Machine\" title=\"Wayback Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>. Inter-Lakes High School</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.uschamber.com/institute/volunteers/class_advisors_roles_and_responsibilities.htm\">\"Class Advisors Roles and Responsibilities\"</a><sup class=\"noprint Inline-Template\"><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">&#91;<i><a href=\"/wiki/Wikipedia:Link_rot\" title=\"Wikipedia:Link rot\"><span title=\"&#160;Dead link since August 2017\">permanent dead link</span></a></i>&#93;</span></sup> US Chamber of Commerce, Institute for Organization Management</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mw1238\nCached time: 20180909114506\nCache expiry: 1900800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.084 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.113 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 335/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 0/1500000\nPost\u2010expand include size: 3564/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 639/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 12/40\nExpensive parser function count: 1/500\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post\u2010expand size: 